    <h3>Getting Involved</h3>
    <p>There are lots of ways to get involved with Euterpea. First, write some programs using Euterpea - the more people who show off their creative talents using Euterpea, the more people will be intersted.</p>
    <p>We also need help with the development of the core language. Try opening bug reports and feature requests on the <a href='https://github.com/Euterpea/Euterpea'>Github</a> page. Maybe even contribute some code. If you want to get involved with the research surrounding Euterpea, let us know! You can contact any one on the research team by going through the Yale Haskell Group's webpage.</p>
    </div>
    

