    <h3>Research</h3>
    <p>Euterpea is a Computer Music language developed by the <a href='http://haskell.cs.yale.edu/'>Yale Haskell Group</a>. A number of publications and talks have stemmed from work on this project. They can be viewed on the Yale Haskell Group's <a href='http://haskell.cs.yale.edu/publications/'>publication's page</a>.</p>
    <h3>This site</h3>
    <p>Even this site is written is Haskell! We are using <a href='http://snapframework.com/'>Snap</a> and might even use Euterpea at somepoint too.</p>
